                   // but this is illegal Java
                   View v = mViewGenerators.get(dataClass).generate(data);

                   // add the view to the growing GUI
                   ...
              }
         }
         ...
    }

You can see what the issue here is. Note that one could potentially use a hack like reflection but as I just said, seems like a hack and a code smell.

Hence, what&#39;s the better way to design or approach this that would not have this problem?

